Package sage.util

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BufferUtils
    This class provides a set of static methods for creating and manipulating java.nio Buffers.
    ColorRGBA
    ColorRGBA defines a color made from a collection of red, green and blue values.
    Debug
    Debug provides a set of static methods that log information for debugging purposes.
    HashCodeUtil
    This class defines a set of methods which allow easy implementation of hashCode().
    MathUtils
    This class contains a variety of math-oriented utility routines.
    VersionInfo
    This class maintains and display Sage version information.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Debug.DebugLevel
    DebugLevel defines the different levels of debug logging there are.
    Debug.ExclusivityLevel
    ExclusivityLevel defines the different levels of logging exclusivity such as only logging messages that belong to the current debug level or logging messages that fall within a range of restriction such as messages between WARN and FATAL debug levels.
